          <p class="text-lg text-ink-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
            System integrators design, build, install, and commission complete conveyor systems. They may manufacture their own conveyors, source equipment from multiple manufacturers, or both. For complex packaging lines with multiple conveyor types, <a href="/conveyor-functions/infeed-outfeed/" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover font-semibold">infeed/outfeed</a> connections, and PLC controls, an integrator is typically the right partner. For a single conveyor purchase, buying direct from a manufacturer is often simpler and less expensive.
